〰️ giveaway time 〰️

giving away a one night stay in a glass cabin at @tututunlodge , my favorite stay ever!!! 🌲 you are going to love it! (spa & dining not included in giveaway) 

here’s how to enter:
1. follow @mariiismith + @tututunlodge 
2. tag three friends in the comments 
3. share this post on your stories for an extra entry & tag @mariiismith + @tututunlodge so we can see your extra entry! 

winner will be announced 1 week from today 6/19 🤭 happy giveaway hehe!
